### VeriFund manual endpoint test file
### Use with VS Code REST Client, JetBrains HTTP Client, or any editor that supports .http files.
### Order matters for the protected flows below.

@gateway = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@ai = http://127.0.0.1:8005
@notify = http://127.0.0.1:8006

### Replace these after you register/login and create records
@token = paste-jwt-here
@cooperativeId = paste-cooperative-id-here
@withdrawalId = paste-withdrawal-id-here
@merchantReference = paste-merchant-reference-here
@testBvn = 123456789

### 1. Register member
POST {{gateway}}/api/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bvn": "{{testBvn}}",
  "first_name": "Ada",
  "last_name": "Okafor",
  "phone_number": "08012345678",
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!123"
}

### 2. Login member
POST {{gateway}}/api/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "08012345678",
  "password": "Passw0rd!123"
}

### 3. Get current member profile
GET {{gateway}}/api/members/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update current member profile
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/members/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Adaobi",
  "email": "adaobi@example.com"
}

### 5. Create cooperative
POST {{gateway}}/api/cooperatives/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lagos Market Women Coop",
  "registration_number": "REG-12345",
  "state": "Lagos",
  "cooperative_type": "MULTIPURPOSE",
  "treasurer_bvn": "{{testBvn}}"
}

### 6. Cooperative detail
GET {{gateway}}/api/cooperatives/{{cooperativeId}}/

### 7. Cooperative trust score
GET {{gateway}}/api/cooperatives/{{cooperativeId}}/trust-score/

### 8. Cooperative regulator summary
GET {{gateway}}/api/cooperatives/{{cooperativeId}}/regulator-summary/

### 9. Create contribution virtual account
POST {{gateway}}/api/contributions/virtual-account/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cooperative_id": "{{cooperativeId}}",
  "bvn": "{{testBvn}}",
  "dob": "07/19/1990",
  "address": "22 Marina Road, Lagos",
  "gender": "1",
  "phone_number": "08012345678",
  "email": "ada@example.com"
}

### 10. List contribution virtual accounts
GET {{gateway}}/api/contributions/virtual-account/list/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Simulate virtual account contribution
POST {{gateway}}/api/contributions/virtual-account/simulate/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cooperative_id": "{{cooperativeId}}",
  "amount_kobo": 500000
}

### 12. Process Squad webhook
POST {{gateway}}/api/webhooks/squad/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Event": "charge_successful",
  "TransactionRef": "WEB-001",
  "Body": {
    "transaction_reference": "WEB-001",
    "virtual_account_number": "9013151601",
    "principal_amount": "7000.00",
    "settled_amount": "7000.00",
    "currency": "NGN",
    "customer_identifier": "VF-F15BD461-105A9639"
  }
}

### 13. Contribution history
GET {{gateway}}/api/contributions/history/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Contribution audit
GET {{gateway}}/api/contributions/audit/{{cooperativeId}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. List webhook events
GET {{gateway}}/api/contributions/webhooks/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. Lookup withdrawal account
POST {{gateway}}/api/withdrawals/lookup/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination_bank_code": "000013",
  "destination_account": "0123456789"
}

### 17. Create withdrawal request
POST {{gateway}}/api/withdrawals/request/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cooperative_id": "{{cooperativeId}}",
  "amount_kobo": 100000,
  "destination_account": "0123456789",
  "destination_bank_code": "000013",
  "purpose": "Emergency member support"
}

### 18. Withdrawal detail
GET {{gateway}}/api/withdrawals/{{withdrawalId}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. Pending withdrawals
GET {{gateway}}/api/withdrawals/pending/?cooperative_id={{cooperativeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 20. Sign withdrawal as EXECUTIVE1 or EXECUTIVE2
POST {{gateway}}/api/withdrawals/{{withdrawalId}}/sign/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "EXECUTIVE1"
}

### 21. Requery withdrawal
POST {{gateway}}/api/withdrawals/{{withdrawalId}}/requery/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 22. AI score transaction
POST {{ai}}/api/ai/score-transaction/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_kobo": 500000,
  "rolling_90d_mean": 300000,
  "days_since_last_contribution": 12,
  "member_transaction_count": 7,
  "cooperative_flagged_rate": 0.05
}

### 23. AI score cooperative
POST {{ai}}/api/ai/score-cooperative/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cooperative_id": "{{cooperativeId}}",
  "breakdown": {
    "contribution_regularity_score": 82,
    "withdrawal_frequency": 2,
    "member_churn_rate": 0.08,
    "avg_transaction_size": 250000,
    "num_large_withdrawals_30d": 0,
    "bvn_verification_rate": 1.0,
    "avg_withdrawal_risk": 0.12,
    "flagged_ratio": 0.03,
    "net_asset_trend_90d": 1200000
  }
}

### 24. AI cooperative score from DB
GET {{ai}}/api/ai/score-cooperative/{{cooperativeId}}/

### 25. AI triage report
POST {{ai}}/api/ai/triage-report/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "report_text": "Suspicious withdrawal missing 50000 from the cooperative wallet",
  "reporter_cooperative_id": "{{cooperativeId}}"
}

### 26. AI graph analysis
POST {{ai}}/api/ai/analyze-graph/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cooperative_id": "{{cooperativeId}}"
}

### 27. AI graph analysis from DB
GET {{ai}}/api/ai/analyze-graph/{{cooperativeId}}/

### 28. AI health scores
GET {{ai}}/api/ai/health-scores/

### 29. AI all health scores
GET {{ai}}/api/ai/health-scores/all/

### 30. Send email notification
POST {{notify}}/api/notify/email/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "member@example.com",
  "subject": "VeriFund notification",
  "message": "VeriFund smoke test"
}

### 31. Notification history
GET {{notify}}/api/notify/history/?limit=5
